    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it since day one, so it\u2019s still got that 'new car' feel inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
