    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained to exacting standards. This chassis retains its factory-spec 13B-REW power plant, featuring a seamless sequential turbocharger transition and verified high-compression rotors. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual transmission and the original Torsen limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full silicone vacuum line refresh and a multi-point inspection of the aluminum double-wishbone suspension components. With zero chassis oxidation and a pristine interior, this FD represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering, offering unparalleled steering feedback and a perfect 50/50 weight distribution for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
