    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream and a rare find for the discerning enthusiast. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and entirely free of creases, while the interior still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions with precision, reflecting a life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from new, featuring a meticulous service history and a ride quality that is both silent and powerful. This is a flawless example of automotive excellence, offering the exact experience of driving it off the lot for the first time.",
      "price": 46500.0,
